Adds the per specification needed 'FN'-property if it's not existing. The string is generated from the 'N'-property.

* Example

$ cd ./dir_with_seperated_vcf_file_in_it/
$ ./fix_vcard.rb ./card1.vcf

or more files at once
$ ./fix_vcard.rb ./card2.vcf ./card3.vcf

or if you want to fix all files in the given directory:
$ ./fix_vcard.rb `./all_vcards.rb`
